{"type": "edit", "field": "information", "label": "Other info", "before": null, "after": "\u2022 Every other Saturday they are open 8:30 PM \u2013 4:30 PM\\n\u2022 Call (844) 692-4692 for an appointment anytime, walk-ins are only allowed in emergencies\\n\u2022 New patients for pediatrics primary care and OBGYN can schedule an appointment online as well\\n\u2022 Current patients can schedule an appointment, speak to a provider, and more at mychart.nychealthandhospitals.org\\n\u2022 Anyone, regardless of insurance status, is welcome\\n\u2022 If you are a Medicaid or Medicare recipient, see if you qualify for a Round-Trip MetroCard upon your visit\\n\u2022 Specialty services require a referral from a primary care provider and many hospitals only serve people with established primary care at the same hospital\\n\u2022 Underage patients require custodial escort", "note": "Added Other info", "summary": "Added Other info", "ts": "2025-09-23T15:35:47.374000Z", "userName": "410370eb-f81b-474e-bdce-ba0994761730", "pagePath": "/team/location/28e0636f-4147-45d2-9c1c-b21f108583e7/services/e7f53802-4ee7-4efe-b12f-07f505140eaa/other-info", "locationId": "28e0636f-4147-45d2-9c1c-b21f108583e7", "serviceId": "e7f53802-4ee7-4efe-b12f-07f505140eaa", "resourceTable": "event_related_info", "action": "create", "copyedit": false}
